divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside in my backyard, when i looked NW and saw an object to the west of Casa Grande Mtn. It was pulsating red,yellow,white. It would get brighter then dimmer. It would disappear then reappear to the east, then disappear and return. Kept pulsating the entire time. Started watching around 8 pm through midnight. It was still there.
Summary: Pulsating 3 lights, hovered,moved, grew brighter then dimmer.
